@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>Welcome to NuocMamBaHai ("us," "we," or "our"). We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about our policy or our practices with regards to your personal information, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].</p>

        <p>When you visit our website and use our services, you trust us with your personal information. We take your privacy very seriously. In this privacy policy, we describe our privacy practices and policies.</p>

        <p>
            <strong>1. Information We Collect</strong><br>
            [List the types of information you collect, e.g., name, email address, payment information, etc.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>2. How We Use Your Information</strong><br>
            [Explain how you use the collected information, e.g., for processing orders, improving our services, sending promotional emails, etc.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>3. How We Protect Your Information</strong><br>
            [Describe the security measures you have in place to protect user data.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>4. Your Privacy Rights</strong><br>
            [Explain the rights users have regarding their personal information, e.g., the right to access, correct, or delete data.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>5. Data Retention</strong><br>
            [Specify how long you retain user data.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>6. Third-Party Links</strong><br>
            [If you have links to third-party websites, explain that your policy does not cover those sites.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>7. Contact Information</strong><br>
            [Provide contact information for privacy-related inquiries.]
        </p>

        <p>
            <strong>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong><br>
            [Explain how you'll notify users of any changes to the privacy policy.]
        </p>

        <p>We hope you take the time to read this policy carefully. If you don't agree with any part of this privacy policy, please do not use our website or services.</p>

        <p>By accessing or using our website, you agree to this privacy policy. Your continued use of our website after we make changes is deemed to be acceptance of those changes.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing [Your Fish Sauce Shop]. We're committed to protecting your privacy and providing you with the best possible experience.</p>

        <p>This privacy policy was last updated on 10/13/2023.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
